<div style="color:Black;background-color:White;"><pre>
   <span style="color:Blue;">var</span> excelApp = <span style="color:Blue;">new</span> ActiveXObject(<span style="color:#A31515;">&quot;Excel.Application&quot;</span>);

  <span style="color:Blue;">var</span> params = { foo: <span style="color:#A31515;">&quot;foo&quot;</span>, bar: 10};
  excelApp.doFoo(params);  
</pre></div>You will probably get better luck with JavaScript related questions on StackOverflow.<br />
